                            <comment id="12992576" author="jbellis" created="Wed, 9 Feb 2011 17:04:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 to the approach.  a couple possible improvements:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;I think all the calls to sendRR(prod.getMessage(Gossiper..), endpoint, handler) can be replaced with sendRR(prod, endpoint, handler)?&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let&apos;s make CMP less wasteful by giving initialcapacity of 2 (common case: everyone is on same versio &amp;#8211; it gets multipled by load factor, so 2 gets rounded down to 1) and making getMessage take an Integer (so we auto&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;un&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;box zero times instead of 4)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12992649" author="gdusbabek" created="Wed, 9 Feb 2011 18:41:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;v2 makes suggested improvements.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
